ng đại phu phá Bá Tiên khải ca kỳ 1 - 獻封大夫破播仙凱歌其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/S%E1%BA%A7m-Tham/author-AcWs16LhWAEAw513Kk2DnA">Sầm Tham</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/Manh-4/poem-CZX4A7xNs4WPs3fFDSW8Cg">Manh 4 - 氓 4</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/author-Ghtg3UHpaIYXCkHiqunT7w">Khổng Tử</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Khi%C3%AAm/T%E1%BB%91ng-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-th%C6%B0-S%C3%A0i-Trang-Khanh-t%E1%BB%B1/poem-zD7mrwO-43MIHObHTaGOMw">Tống thượng thư Sài Trang Khanh tự - 送尚書柴莊卿序</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Khi%C3%AAm/author-1_5YGABQESnAmYdOvhbEZQ">Lý Khiêm</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-V%C5%A9-X%E1%BB%A9ng/Xu%C3%A2n-nh%E1%BA%ADt-%C4%91%C4%83ng-l%C3%A2u/poem-69IZBNdBG4bgdUgTD6w8zw">Xuân nhật đăng lâu - 春日登樓</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-V%C5%A9-X%E1%BB%A9ng/author-gsSbrX8mxDOHV8mbduxYMg">Vương Vũ Xứng</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Duy/Y%C3%AAn-Chi-h%C3%A0nh/poem-3E00fLMXNpzWXZkyeUTVMQ">Yên Chi hành - 燕支行</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Duy/author-9f1Hth0gmM_PXzGNXg5Fog">Vương Duy</a>)<br></div>	</div>
